===Etymology===
From [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[蟽蟿苇蠁伪谓慰蟼]]''' (''stefanos'') "that which surrounds or encompasses, a crown, wreath, chaplet", from  '''[[蟽蟿苇蠁蠅]]''' (''stefo'') "to put round, to surround".

